sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor U as User
participant FE as Frontend
participant AIC as AIController
participant AIS as AIService
participant W as PendingActionWorkflow
participant DS as DomainService
participant DB as Domain data
participant LOG as AI Log

U->>FE: Ask AI to perform a write action
FE->>AIC: Send chat/tool request
AIC->>AIS: Analyze request and tool call
AIS->>W: Create pending action with preview and params
W->>LOG: Record pending action
W-->>AIS: actionId and summary
AIS-->>FE: Confirmation required
FE-->>U: Show Confirm / Cancel

alt User confirms
  U->>FE: Confirm action
  FE->>AIC: POST /ai/actions/confirm
  AIC->>W: Check ownership, session, expiry
  W->>DS: Execute write action
  DS->>DB: Update domain data
  DB-->>DS: Updated
  DS-->>W: Execution result
  W->>LOG: Record confirmed result
  W-->>FE: Success
  FE-->>U: Show updated state
else User cancels
  U->>FE: Cancel action
  FE->>AIC: POST /ai/actions/cancel
  AIC->>W: Mark action canceled
  W->>LOG: Record cancellation
  W-->>FE: Canceled
end
